    "created_at": "2012-07-17T23:58:53Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-07-17T23:58:53Z",
    "body": "Fixing this bug will make this no longer segfault.\n\n```\nconst generations: uint = 1024+256+128+49;\n\nfn child_no(x: uint) -> fn~() {\n    ret || {\n        if x < generations {\n            task::spawn(child_no(x+1));\n        }\n    }\n}\n\nfn main() {\n    task::spawn(child_no(0));\n}\n```\n",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
