    "updated_at": "2012-07-18T00:11:12Z",
    "body": "Also, after fixing this, I believe nothing will ever refcount a task apart from itself (well, its sched_loop is the one that derefs it, but same thing)?\n\nI'll leave the refcount in in case it's needed for work stealing, I think. It's an atomic operation but it won't cost anything because it never contends.\n",
